\c 6
\p
\v 1 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuMozisi: Khathesi uzabona engizakwenza kuFaro; ngoba ngesandla esilamandla uzabayekela bahambe\x + 3.19.\x*, langesandla esilamandla uzabaxotsha elizweni lakhe\x + 11.1; 12.39.\x*.
\s UMozisi ubizwa ngokwesibili
\p
\v 2 UNkulunkulu wasekhuluma kuMozisi wathi kuye: NgiyiN\nd kosi\nd*;
\v 3 njalo ngabonakala kuAbrahama, kuIsaka, lakuJakobe njengoNkulunkulu uSomandla\x + Gen. 17.1.\x*; kodwa ngebizo lami \add lokuthi\add* uJehova ngangingaziwa kubo\x + 3.14; 15.2. Hlab. 68.4; 83.18. Joha. 8.58. Isam. 1.4,8.\x*.
\v 4 Njalo lami ngamisa isivumelwano sami labo\x + Gen. 15.18; 17.4,7.\x* ukubapha ilizwe leKhanani\x + Gen. 17.8; 28.4.\x*, ilizwe lobuhambuma babo, ababehlala kulo njengabezizwe.
\v 5 Futhi lami ngizwile ukububula kwabantwana bakoIsrayeli, amaGibhithe abagcine ebugqilini; njalo ngikhumbule isivumelwano sami\x + 2.24.\x*.
\v 6 Ngakho-ke tshono kubantwana bakoIsrayeli \add ukuthi\add*: NgiyiN\nd kosi\x + 6.2.\x*\nd*; njalo ngizalikhupha lisuke ngaphansi kwemithwalo yamaGibhithe\x + 7.4. Dute. 26.8. Hlab. 136.11,12.\x*; ngilikhulule ebugqilini bawo, ngilihlenge ngengalo eyeluliweyo langezigwebo ezinkulu\x + 15.13. Gen. 48.16.\x*.
\v 7 Njalo ngizazithathela lina libe yisizwe\x + Dute. 4.20.\x*, ngizakuba kini nguNkulunkulu\x + 29.45,46. Gen. 17.8. Dute. 29.13. Isam. 21.7.\x*; njalo lizakwazi ukuthi ngiyiN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu, olikhupha lisuke ngaphansi kwemithwalo yamaGibhithe\x + 6.6; 5.4,5. Hlab. 81.6.\x*;
\v 8 njalo ngizalingenisa elizweni engaphakamisa isandla sami ngalo ukulinika uAbrahama, uIsaka loJakobe, ngilinike lona libe yilifa\x + Gen. 26.3.\x*; mina, iN\nd kosi\nd*.
\v 9 UMozisi wasekhuluma ngokunjalo kubantwana bakoIsrayeli; kodwa kabamlalelanga uMozisi\x + 5.21.\x* ngenxa yokukhathazeka komoya langenxa yobugqili obunzima.
\p
\v 10 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhuluma kuMozisi isithi:
\v 11 Ngena ukhulume kuFaro, inkosi yeGibhithe, ukuthi ayekele abantwana bakoIsrayeli basuke elizweni lakhe.
\v 12 Kodwa uMozisi wakhuluma phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd* esithi: Khangela, abantwana bakoIsrayeli kabangilalelanga\x + 6.9.\x*; pho-ke uFaro angangizwa njani, engingowendebe ezingasokanga\x + 4.10; 6.30. Levi 26.41. Jer. 6.10; 9.26. Hez. 44.7. Seb. 7.51. Levi 19.23. Jer. 1.6. Roma 2.29. Kol. 2.11.\x*?
\p
\v 13 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhuluma kuMozisi lakuAroni yabapha umlayo ngabantwana bakoIsrayeli langoFaro inkosi yeGibhithe ukukhupha abantwana bakoIsrayeli elizweni leGibhithe.
\s Inzalo kaMozisi lenzalo kaAroni
\p
\v 14 Laba bazinhloko zezindlu zaboyise; amadodana kaRubeni, izibulo likaIsrayeli: OHanoki loPalu, oHezironi loKarimi; laba bazinsapho zikaRubeni\x + Gen. 46.9. 1 Lan. 5.3.\x*.
\v 15 Lamadodana kaSimeyoni: OJemuweli loJamini loOhadi loJakini loZohari loShawuli indodana yomKhananikazi; laba bazinsapho zikaSimeyoni\x + Gen. 46.10. 1 Lan. 4.24.\x*.
\p
\v 16 Njalo la ngamabizo amadodana kaLevi ngezizukulwana zawo\x + Gen. 46.11. Nani 3.17. 1 Lan. 6.1,16.\x*: OGerishoni loKohathi loMerari; leminyaka yempilo kaLevi yayiyiminyaka elikhulu lamatshumi amathathu lesikhombisa\x + 6.18,20. Gen. 47.28; 50.22.\x*.
\v 17 Amadodana kaGerishoni\x + Nani 3.18. 1 Lan. 6.17; 23.7.\x*: OLibini loShimeyi ngezinsapho zawo.
\v 18 Njalo amadodana kaKohathi\x + Nani 3.19; 26.57. 1 Lan. 6.2,18.\x*: OAmramu loIzihari loHebroni loUziyeli; leminyaka yempilo kaKohathi yayiyiminyaka elikhulu lamatshumi amathathu lantathu.
\v 19 Njalo amadodana kaMerari\x + Nani 3.20. 1 Lan. 6.19; 23.21.\x*: OMahli loMushi. Laba bazinsapho zamaLevi ngezizukulwana zabo.
\v 20 UAmramu wasethatha uJokebedi udadewabo kayise, waba ngumka\add khe\add*. Wasemzalela uAroni loMozisi\x + 2.1,2. Nani 26.59.\x*. Leminyaka yempilo kaAmramu yayiyiminyaka elikhulu lamatshumi amathathu lesikhombisa.
\v 21 Njalo amadodana kaIzihari: OKora loNefegi loZikiri\x + Nani 16.1. 1 Lan. 6.37,38.\x*.
\v 22 Lamadodana kaUziyeli: OMishayeli loElizafani loSithiri\x + Levi 10.4. Nani 3.30.\x*.
\v 23 UAroni wasezithathela uElisheba indodakazi kaAminadaba\x + Ruthe 4.19,20. 1 Lan. 2.10. Mat. 1.4. Luka 3.33.\x*, udadewabo kaNashoni\x + Nani 1.7; 2.3; 7.12,17; 10.14. Mat. 1.4. Luka 3.32.\x*, waba ngumka\add khe\add*. Wasemzalela uNadabi loAbihu, uEleyazare loIthamari\x + Levi 10.1. Nani 3.2; 26.60. 1 Lan. 6.3; 24.1.\x*.
\v 24 Njalo amadodana kaKora: OAsiri loElkana loAbhiyasafa; laba bazinsapho zabakoKora\x + 1 Lan. 6.22.\x*.
\v 25 UEleyazare indodana kaAroni wasezithathela enye yamadodakazi kaPutiyeli, yaba ngumka\add khe\add*. Yasimzalela uPhinehasi\x + Nani 25.7,11. Josh. 24.33. Hlab. 106.30.\x*. Yizo lezi inhloko zaboyise bamaLevi ngezinsapho zazo.
\v 26 Lo nguAroni loMozisi iN\nd kosi\nd* eyathi kubo\x + 6.13.\x*: Khuphani abantwana bakoIsrayeli elizweni leGibhithe ngamabutho abo\x + 7.4; 12.17,41,51. Nani 33.1.\x*.
\v 27 Yibo labo ababekhuluma kuFaro inkosi yeGibhithe\x + 5.1,3; 7.10.\x* ukukhupha abantwana bakoIsrayeli eGibhithe; lo nguMozisi loAroni.
\s INkosi iyabalaya oMozisi loAroni
\p
\v 28 Kwasekusithi mhla iN\nd kosi\nd* ikhuluma kuMozisi elizweni leGibhithe
\v 29 iN\nd kosi\nd* yakhuluma kuMozisi isithi: Mina ngiyiN\nd kosi\x + 6.2.\x*\nd*; khuluma kuFaro inkosi yeGibhithe konke engikukhuluma kuwe\x + 6.11; 7.2.\x*.
\v 30 UMozisi wasesithi phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*: Khangela, ngingowendebe ezingasokanga\x + 6.12.\x*; ngakho uFaro angangizwa njani?